Class Ajax4jsfFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.seam.web.AbstractFilter
      • org.jboss.seam.web.Ajax4jsfFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.Filter

    @Scope(value=APPLICATION)
 @Name(value="org.jboss.seam.web.ajax4jsfFilter")
 @Install(precedence=0,
         dependencies="org.jboss.seam.web.ajax4jsfFilterInstantiator")
 @BypassInterceptors
 @Filter
public class Ajax4jsfFilter
extends AbstractFilter
    A Seam filter component wrapper for the Ajax4JSF. This class exists to allow the Ajax4JSF filter to be configured in the web: namespace. The subclass does the actual work. See org.jboss.seam.ui.filter.Ajax4jsfFilterInstantiator
    Author:
    Pete Muir
